    <!-- Shooting Tips -->
    <string name="tips_fuji_film">[Environment] Daylight outdoor or well-lit indoor&#10;[Scenes] Street, portrait, landscape, architecture&#10;[Tips] Classic film aesthetic with rich, vintage colors. Look for scenes with light-shadow contrast to enhance depth</string>
    <string name="tips_film_feel">[Environment] Natural or soft artificial light&#10;[Scenes] Portraits, still life, cafés, artistic scenes&#10;[Tips] Soft light creates dreamy atmosphere. Perfect for emotional photos. Keep the subject in sharp focus</string>
    <string name="tips_fairy_tale">[Environment] Morning, dusk or overcast diffused light&#10;[Scenes] Children, gardens, parks, romantic scenes&#10;[Tips] Darker tones create mystery. Dreamy soft light for fairy tale vibes. Seek colorful scenes</string>
    <string name="tips_high_contrast_bw">[Environment] Strong light-shadow contrast, direct sunlight or spotlights&#10;[Scenes] Architecture, documentary, street, artistic portraits&#10;[Tips] Use contrast to highlight subject contours. Perfect for geometric lines and rich textures. Keep composition clean</string>
    <string name="tips_ricoh_green">[Environment] Natural outdoor light, forests, meadows, plant-rich scenes&#10;[Scenes] Plants, forest walks, spring outdoors, fresh portraits&#10;[Tips] Bright tones highlight freshness. Greens appear natural and transparent. Perfect for plants and nature</string>
    <string name="tips_ricoh_blue">[Environment] Sunny weather or blue sky background&#10;[Scenes] Seaside, urban architecture, sky, cool-toned scenes&#10;[Tips] Cool tones enhance blue performance. Perfect for sky, water and urban architecture. Creates transparent, calm atmosphere</string>
    <string name="tips_blue_hour">[Environment] 20 minutes before sunrise or after sunset&#10;[Scenes] City night views, bright lights, water reflections&#10;[Tips] Strong warm-cool contrast. Perfect for city lights and night scenes. Seek water surfaces for reflection effects</string>
    <string name="tips_dreamy_blackmist">[Environment] Backlit or side-lit scenes&#10;[Scenes] Portraits, emotional photography, artistic scenes, soft beauty&#10;[Tips] Black mist filter creates dreamy atmosphere. Perfect for beautiful portraits. Use backlight for halo effects</string>
    <string name="tips_fuji_nc">[Environment] Daylight outdoor or ample natural light&#10;[Scenes] Japanese-style portraits, street, daily records, travel&#10;[Tips] Simulates Fuji NC film. Bright tones, soft natural colors. Perfect for daily records and Japanese aesthetics</string>
    <string name="tips_humanities">[Environment] Natural or soft artificial light&#10;[Scenes] Street documentary, humanistic photography, life records, storytelling&#10;[Tips] Pro mode with fixed parameters. ISO 50 ensures pure image quality. Slight underexposure preserves details. Perfect for capturing real life moments</string>
    <string name="tips_fresh_humanities">[Environment] Bright outdoor or indoor natural light&#10;[Scenes] Fresh Japanese portraits, campus, travel, daily life&#10;[Tips] Bright tones, higher saturation. Perfect for fresh, bright portraits and scenes. Seek well-lit scenes</string>
    <string name="tips_snowy_night">[Environment] Snowy, overcast or low color temperature scenes&#10;[Scenes] Snow scenes, winter streets, warm indoor, festive atmosphere&#10;[Tips] Warm tones balance snow\'s coolness. Creates cozy atmosphere. Perfect for winter scenes and warm light environments</string>
    <string name="tips_delicious">[Environment] Restaurants, kitchens, food photography scenes&#10;[Scenes] Food photography, beverages, baking, fine cuisine&#10;[Tips] Darker tones highlight food texture. Moderate saturation keeps food\'s true colors. Perfect for fine food and beverages</string>
    <string name="tips_mobile_leica">[Environment] Daylight outdoor or ample light&#10;[Scenes] Street, architecture, landscape, daily records&#10;[Tips] Simulates Leica\'s German style. Deep tones, restrained colors. Perfect for photography enthusiasts seeking Leica aesthetics</string>
    <string name="tips_dreamy_fuji">[Environment] Daylight outdoor or soft light&#10;[Scenes] Portraits, landscapes, Japanese scenes, artistic photography&#10;[Tips] Pro mode auto exposure. Slight overexposure creates dreamy feel. Vintage tones with dreamy soft light. Perfect for beautiful portraits and landscapes</string>
    <string name="tips_hasselblad_rich">[Environment] Well-lit outdoor or indoor&#10;[Scenes] Landscapes, architecture, portraits, artistic photography&#10;[Tips] Simulates Hasselblad Natural Color Solution. Rich but true-to-life colors. Perfect for high-quality color performance</string>
    <string name="tips_holiday_fresh">[Environment] Sunny weather or bright vacation scenes&#10;[Scenes] Seaside, vacation, travel, summer outdoors&#10;[Tips] Bright and transparent tones. Lower saturation creates freshness. Perfect for vacation and travel scenes. Capture joyful moments</string>
    <string name="tips_dreamy_bw">[Environment] Soft light or overcast&#10;[Scenes] Emotional portraits, artistic photography, still life, architecture&#10;[Tips] Retains slight color information. Dreamy soft light creates artistic feel. Perfect for expressive black and white photography</string>
    <string name="tips_delicious_dream">[Environment] Restaurants, cafés, cozy indoor&#10;[Scenes] Food, desserts, beverages, delicate items&#10;[Tips] Dreamy soft light creates warm atmosphere. Darker tones highlight texture. Perfect for fine food and cozy scenes</string>
    <string name="tips_blue_clear">[Environment] Daylight outdoor or indoor, seaside, sky, water surface&#10;[Scenes] Landscapes, architecture, portraits, still life&#10;[Tips] Blue clarity style with cool tones creates fresh and transparent feel. Slight underexposure preserves details. Dreamy soft light adds atmosphere. Perfect for fresh landscapes and portraits</string>
    <string name="tips_sunny_vintage">[Environment] Sunny outdoor, well-lit scenes&#10;[Scenes] Street, portraits, landscapes, vintage scenes&#10;[Tips] Sunny vintage style with 5000K color temp for natural colors. Negative tone creates vintage feel. Slight underexposure preserves highlight details. Warm soft light adds retro atmosphere. Perfect for sunny outdoor portraits and landscapes</string>
    <string name="tips_neon_lights">[Environment] Night city, neon signs, bustling streets&#10;[Scenes] Night views, street scenes, portraits, urban landscapes&#10;[Tips] Neon lights style with rich filter enhancing color saturation. Gentle soft light creates dreamy feel. Slight underexposure preserves neon details. Perfect for night city neon scenes</string>
    <string name="tips_retro_nostalgia">[Environment] Old districts, vintage scenes, nostalgic indoor settings&#10;[Scenes] Old objects, street scenes, portraits, storytelling scenes&#10;[Tips] Retro nostalgia style with 65% vintage filter for nostalgic feel. Low tone adds retro atmosphere. Reduced saturation simulates old photo texture. Perfect for nostalgic themed photos</string>

